title: Miele C3 Alize Canister Vacuum
description:
In this video we take a closer look at the Miele C3ALIZE canister vacuum.  For more details or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/product/88838/Miele-C3-Alize-Ivory-White-Canister-Vacuum-41GJE031USA.html?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=video&utm_campaign=C3ALIZE%20_2017077 

Features:
Silence motor with 6 speed settings controlled via +/- footswitch controls
Automatic speed control setting
Spotlight handle
36' operating radius
HEPA AirClean filter
SBD 650-3 AirTeq floor brush
Recommended for low pile carpeting, rugs, & hard floors
